<p>&#8220;Open the kimono&#8221; is a popular corporate lingo that means to be transparent with a partner or buyer about exact numbers and facts. It means to reveal; to show the other party where you&#8217;re vulnerable, weak, and may fall apart. In other words, being naked is partially about being ugly.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/SchrodingrsBrat/status/1623332457859756033" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png" width="548" height="183.279128248114" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/cd88b5a1-9f7a-4b50-9650-83e0c74adc58_1193x399.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:399,&quot;width&quot;:1